@startuml 图4-3 审核流程时序图
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontColor #000000

actor "审核员" as Auditor
participant "EduAuditRecord\nController" as Ctrl
participant "IEduAuditRecord\nService" as AuditSvc
participant "IEduAchievement\nService" as AchSvc
participant "MySQL" as DB

== 审核员查看待审成果 ==
Auditor -> Ctrl : GET /audit/record/list
Ctrl -> AuditSvc : 查询待审成果(status=2)
AuditSvc -> DB : SELECT * FROM edu_achievement\nWHERE status='2'
DB --> AuditSvc : 列表数据
AuditSvc --> Ctrl : List<Achievement>
Ctrl --> Auditor : 渲染审核列表

== 审核员审核通过 ==
Auditor -> Ctrl : POST /audit/record/approve\n{achievementId, opinion}

Ctrl -> Ctrl : 构建审核记录\n(auditor_id, auditor_name,\naudit_result=1, opinion)

Ctrl -> AuditSvc : approve(achievementId, auditRecord)

AuditSvc -> AchSvc : updateAchievement\n(setStatus=3)

AchSvc -> DB : UPDATE edu_achievement\nSET status='3'\nWHERE achievement_id=?

AuditSvc -> DB : INSERT INTO edu_audit_record\n(audit_result='1', opinion, ...)

DB --> AuditSvc : success
AuditSvc --> Ctrl : success
Ctrl --> Auditor : 审核通过，已公示

note over Ctrl, DB
  状态更新和记录插入在同一事务中
  通过@Transactional保证原子性
end note

@enduml
